{
  "texts": [
    "Explicit definition of specific use-cases/tasks for a given disease.",
    "Identification of specific data types required for each use case, whether that data currently exists in some form or will be available in the future to meet the capabilities of an aspirational MDT.",
    "Of note, obtaining time series/ongoing collected data is essential to this step, as the concept of time-evolution of the MDT is inherent to its definition. 3.",
    "These first three steps should be integrated into a detailed \"roadmap\"",
    "for the development and deployment of the MDT. 4."
  ]
